    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "it's not even just the career stuff. it's that the people i was... the person i thought i was... that person was built on this lie. i look in the mirror and i don't see a scientist, i just see a fraud. i feel like i'm just taking up space that doesn't belong to me anymore. like i'm just a hollow shell of a mistake.",
